text: Katherine Lineth Castillo Macías (born 23 March 1996) is a Panamanian footballer who plays as a midfielder for the Panama women's national team. ==International career== Castillo appeared in four matches for Panama at the 2018 CONCACAF Women's Championship. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Panamanian women's footballers Category:Panama women's international footballers Category:Pan American Games competitors for Panama Category:Footballers at the 2019 Pan American Games
